components.name: Extract Mahidol AQI HTML

inputs: Existing JSON file for duplicate detection (if any)

components.name: Load Mahidol AQI into PostgreSQL
components.description: Inserts the parsed AQI JSON into PostgreSQL dimension and fact tables using upsert logic.

components.description: Sends email notifications via SMTP when PM2.5 AQI exceeds defined thresholds; skips if AQI is within safe range.
